Base
- Add text blocks to the dashboard to provide supplementary information or explanations, giving your audience the context they need to interpret the data.
- Generate a query page in Base to make it easy for everyone to find what they need without getting lost in the complexity of the table. Querying survey responses, event registration status, exam scores, and more no longer have to be difficult.
Messenger
- You can group apps and document tabs together to keep the navigation bar organized.

多维表格
- 在仪表盘中可添加文本组件，为仪表盘数据提供补充说明，信息解读更清晰
- 多维表格新增结果查询页，你可将数据表一键生成查询页面，适用于问卷结果查询、活动报名状态查询、考试成绩查询等多场景需求。无需接触复杂数据表，人人都可轻松完成信息查询
即时消息
- 你可将固定在导航栏的内容进行分组整理，让导航栏结构层次更清晰
